      "body": "I managed to reproduce this problem locally. The problem is indeed in propagation:\n\n```\nB1: 204 blocks\nB2: 204 blocks\nB3: 203 blocks\n```\n\nI'm going to add a function `WaitBlocks` that waits until all three nodes have the same amount of blocks, and replace that for the `sleep 1`s.\n",
